Description: Only the most insidious Mastermind could construct such an army.  Cold and relentless, these Bots obey only one voice, and will execute any order without hesitation.

Powers.DescShort: Auto Res Sleep, Fear, Disorient, Lethal, Cold, Psionic
Powers.DescLong: Robots are resistant to Sleep, Fear, and Disorient.  They are also resistant to Lethal, Cold, and Psionic damage. It has a Plasma Blast and melee Smash attack.
Plasma burns are hard to heal.  The burns have halted your Regeneration rate.
The Assault Bot has Disoriented you.
